{"tid":699964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"攻心計！川普給金正恩看棄核後北韓繁榮景象影片","createTime":"2018-06-13T03:10:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T07:40:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d09b3d4aee835d4f1f8cc2e608d58686969ef8ce","tid":699964,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:10:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_php3JXKOb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_php3JXKOb.jpg&h=e831ff1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n川普和金正恩上演世界之握。（美聯社）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n2018-06-13 07:23<br />\r\n<br />\r\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕「川金會」昨天落幕，美國總統川普向北韓領導人金正恩釋出善意，會前還拿出iPad播放影片，給金正恩看了一部4分鐘的好萊塢風格影片，畫面主要表達北韓棄核後會出現的繁榮景象。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpPWWtDB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpPWWtDB.jpg&h=b89c7461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n川普送給北韓的演片展示，北韓未來繁榮的景象。（圖擷自YouTube）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpqEvKfn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpqEvKfn.jpg&h=ea63c1ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n影片中北韓公民相當開心。（圖擷自YouTube）<br />\r\n<br />\r\n綜合外媒報導，川普在峰會開始前向金正恩團隊用韓、英雙語播放北韓繁榮景象的影片；川普表示，「這是我們給金正恩和北韓人民的一段影片，影片中的畫面都是可以實現的！（北韓）是一個很棒的地方」。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n影片主要由資料片段及過往新聞片段組成，影片中出現兩國兩導人，彷彿預視北韓棄核後會出現的繁榮景象，旁白提到，「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>過去不等於未來，新世界可由今天開始。</strong></span>」最後結束的標題則寫道，「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>未來還有待改寫！</strong></span>」<br />\r\n<br />\r\n川普表示，「<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>我相信他（金正恩）會喜歡這片段。</strong></span>」美國政府則說，已將短片備份送給北韓。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n相關影片請見：<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A838gS8nwas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DA838gS8nwas&d=FVhtRRrTkXeh5v7gDiq%2B6zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7345c059\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=A838gS8nwas</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/WhiteHouse/videos/1710505219037204/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FWhiteHouse%2Fvideos%2F1710505219037204%2F&d=FVhtRRrTkXeh5v7gDiq%2B6zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=1636fcc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/WhiteHouse/videos/1710505219037204/</a><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2456359\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2456359&d=FVhtRRrTkXeh5v7gDiq%2B6zPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=6727c02f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2456359&h=cf2eea67\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2456359</a>"},{"pid":"5ffb1e3793488ed1f494ff06232dabda3a247358","tid":699964,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:16:52.000Z","msg":"金仔：<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f6526ee3dec3f5a462b0778ed93191f0fd0044e","tid":699964,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:27:56.000Z","msg":"VHS 帶？"},{"pid":"cfaeb8793995dde79f2feef17c97bc8a33d4bdc4","tid":699964,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:54:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"974d86c3932b0bc7ed9cf674e4ddc41014916d3c","tid":699964,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:27:52.000Z","msg":"痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果條片靚到"},{"pid":"fdaf6b234965b93f8b7bd5f9d6b0aae32affbe66","tid":699964,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:29:00.000Z","msg":"呃細路仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi